All Implemented Interfaces:
MessageFilter
public class ExportUsernameTokenFilter
extends FilterBase
implements MessageFilter

Exports a Username token by prepending a wsse:Username subtree containing a username and password to the wsse:Security header block. This filter requires the following parameters during initialization 1. username : the username 2. password : the password 3. gennonceandcreated : if nonce and created to be generated 4. digestpassword : if password has to be digested

See Also:
ImportUsernameTokenFilter
